### Microservicio: Typing Service
# @baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Check Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Root info
GET {{baseUrl}}/

# ============ VM CLASSES ============

### Listar todas las VM Classes
GET {{baseUrl}}/vm-classes

### Obtener VM Class por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/vm-classes/1

### Crear nueva VM Class
POST {{baseUrl}}/vm-classes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Custom-Gold",
  "description": "Configuración personalizada Gold",
  "cpu_cores": 16,
  "memory_mb": 32768,
  "storage_gb": 1000,
  "cpu_reservation_percent": 75,
  "memory_reservation_percent": 75,
  "provisioning_type": "thick",
  "storage_policy": "Gold-Policy"
}

### Actualizar VM Class
PUT {{baseUrl}}/vm-classes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gold-Updated",
  "description": "Actualizada para producción",
  "cpu_reservation_percent": 80
}

### Bloquear VM Class (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/vm-classes/1/lock

### Desbloquear VM Class (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/vm-classes/1/unlock

### Eliminar VM Class (Soft Delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/vm-classes/3

# ============ TYPIFICATIONS ============

### Crear typification template
POST {{baseUrl}}/templates
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Servidores-Web",
  "prefijo1": "SRV",
  "prefijo2": "WEB",
  "seq_digits": 3
}

### Listar templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/templates

### Previsualizar nombre de VM
POST {{baseUrl}}/generate-name/1?manual_value=proyecto1
